column5: Anyone ever fish North Gull Lake on the Cat River? If so, how did you do?
Thè whole cat river system is fantastic for fishing.the north and south gull outposts were bought last fall by Clarks Outposts so they have 4 outposts along that system now.both qualitý and quantity.
Thanks. We have been to Clarks places the last 3 years. Indian Chain first and then the past 2 years at Anishinabi.
You'll have a blast george. John.
